description: Rottneros AB engages in the production and sale of chemical and mechanical pulp. The firm produces paper pulp at two pulp mills: the Vallvik Mill and the Rottneros Mill. The Vallvik Mill produces two grades of long-fiber sulphate pulp: fully bleached sulphate pulp (ECF - Elemental Chlorine Free) and unbleached sulphate pulp (UKP - Unbleached Kraft Pulp). The Rottneros Mill manufactures mechanical pulp (CTMP) and groundwood pulp. Additionally, the Company produces food packaging. The firm's pulp mainly used for personal care products, filters, board containers, print materials, insulation applications, among others. The firm is active primarily in Germany, Italy, Sweden and the United States, among others.
name: Rottneros AB
